<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/cursor') %>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="cs-hero cs-hero-adum">
    <div class="cs-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="cs-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="cs-hero-content">
      <span class="cs-hero-eyebrow">Case Study</span>
      <h1 class="cs-hero-title">Adum</h1>
      <p class="cs-hero-sub">Music Promotion — Cross-Platform Content</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="cs-stats">
    <div class="cs-stats-inner">
      <div class="cs-stat reveal">
        <span class="cs-stat-num">700K+</span>
        <span class="cs-stat-label">TikTok & YouTube Views</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-stat reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="cs-stat-num">25K+</span>
        <span class="cs-stat-label">Instagram Likes</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-stat reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="cs-stat-num">3</span>
        <span class="cs-stat-label">Shoot Days</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Artist Links -->
  <div class="cs-artist-links reveal">
    <span class="cs-artist-label">Follow Adum</span>
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@adumxo" target="_blank" class="cs-artist-link" aria-label="YouTube">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/></svg>
    </a>
    <a href="https://adum.komi.io/" target="_blank" class="cs-artist-link" aria-label="Komi">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Media -->
  <section class="cs-media">
    <div class="cs-media-grid">
      <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@adumxo/video/7259064047201553691" target="_blank" class="cs-media-item cs-media-link reveal">
        <img src="/images/adum-sing-1.jpg" alt="Adum — TikTok">
        <div class="cs-media-play"><svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="rgba(0,0,0,0.4)"/><polygon points="20,16 34,24 20,32" fill="white"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CnUvQnaIdMu/" target="_blank" class="cs-media-item cs-media-link reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <img src="/images/adum-wk.jpg" alt="Adum — Instagram Reel">
        <div class="cs-media-play"><svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="rgba(0,0,0,0.4)"/><polygon points="20,16 34,24 20,32" fill="white"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cvm9EuENiv8/" target="_blank" class="cs-media-item cs-media-link reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <img src="/images/adum-sing-2.jpg" alt="Adum — Instagram Reel">
        <div class="cs-media-play"><svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="rgba(0,0,0,0.4)"/><polygon points="20,16 34,24 20,32" fill="white"/></svg></div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About the Production -->
  <section class="cs-content">
    <div class="cs-content-inner reveal">
      <div class="cs-content-left">
        <span class="cs-content-eyebrow">The Production</span>
        <h2 class="cs-content-heading">How We<br>Built It</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-content-right">
        <p>Braxton Studios developed a cross-platform content strategy for Adum, creating a suite of short-form assets designed to maximise reach across TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube. Each piece was tailored to the platform — optimising for algorithm-friendly formats, trending audio, and audience engagement patterns.</p>
        <p>From concept through to final delivery, our team handled filming, editing, and platform-specific formatting. The content leaned into bold visuals and rhythmic editing to complement Adum's sound and identity as an artist.</p>
        <p>The campaign delivered standout results — surpassing 700,000 views on TikTok and generating over 25,000 likes on Instagram — proving that a production-first approach to music promotion drives real, measurable impact.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <%- include('partials/scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
